data.description: Nestled in Crestwood, IL, this 3-bed, 2.5-bath home with a 2.5-car garage is move in ready. Two spacious living areas offer versatility, complemented by a freshly painted kitchen for culinary enthusiasts.    Recent updates elevate this home, ensuring peace of mind. A sump pump under 6 years, new windows, a 2-year-old water heater, an AC unit and HVAC under 5 years, a roof under 15 years old, and a sliding door under 3 years old showcase a commitment to quality living.    The fully updated family room downstairs  featuring modern flooring, paint, and a sleek bathroom, adds contemporary flair. Convenience is at your doorstep, with shopping, schools, parks, and forest preserves nearby. This Crestwood gem is more than a home; it's a haven for cherished moments. Don't miss out on this blend of style and functionality-your dream home awaits!
